Hello viewer!!,
This is a fictitious band website [ by the name THE GENESIS ] consisting of 3 webpages integrated well.
TECH STACK -  HTML , CSS , JAVASCRIPT , NODE JS , EXPRESS & MONGODB

DEPENDENCIES INCLUDED ARE LISTED IN THE PACKAGE-JSON FILE

A proper register-login system has been introduced powered with JWT authentication
-> change password feature with email link validation ( nodemailer ) is in production & will be out soon

FEATURES NOT FUNCTIONAL ARE :
  ADD TO CART IN STORE PAGE,
  GET TICKETS IN THE TOURS PAGE,
  CART FUNCTIONALITY.
  change password feature with email link validation ( nodemailer )
  
FEATURES IN THE PIPELINE ARE AS FOLLOWS:
  INTRODUCTION OF JAVASCRIPT TO GET THROUGH ALL NOT FUNCTIONING BUTTONS
  INTRODUCTION OF PAYMENTS ( USING A SUPPORT BUTTON )
  
  FEEL FREE TO PUT IN CLONE REQUESTS INTO THE PROJECT :)
